game.name: Green Lake
game.description:
Like many others, you are fond of fishing when you have some free time to enjoy and kill your boring hours. We are happy to announce you a brand new sports game where you can enjoy your time by discovering the most beautiful fishing areas. Grab your tool and be prepared to catch as man fishes as you can to become a champion in Green Lake! Keep your eyes on both small and big fish, and catch them all to collect all the improvements!

You would a new place, a rod and many other exciting lures to grab. Do not forget to put on your lucky hat, pack your baits and a wonderful fishing rod before going out for fishing. Catching the biggest fish available in the lake will allow you to be the master angler in this HTML5 fishing game! Let the big fish come and bite your bait to grab it fast! You would have multiple baits to use to catch fish and score high on the board.

Get ready to click, and drag the pointer around the lake while keeping your eyes on the bobber in this cool fish game! The bobber will automatically move when your bait gets connected with a fish. It is amazing to earn money with your every successful fish catch. Track your money by looking at the top left side of the screen! Do not forget to purchase new fishing rods, baits and new places for fishing with the help of money you have collected throughout the gameplay. Catch free fishing games on atmegame.com and have fun without download!
